OL,3,C'I'm the boss', says Trump as he meets
OL,4,CG7 leaders on last day of summit
OL,6,FThe White House has reposted a video
OL,7,Fof the moment US President Donald
OL,8,FTrump arrived at the G7 summit for a
OL,9,Fmeeting on Wednesday and told other
OL,10,Fworld leaders, "I am the boss."
OL,12,FThe president made the joke as he
OL,13,Farrived late to a morning meeting on
OL,14,Fthe last of the three-day summit in
OL,15,FEvian-les-Bains, France.
OL,17,FThe joke was met with laughter,
OL,18,Fincluding from Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,19,FStarmer and French President Emmanuel
OL,20,FMacron, who responded by saying: "How
OL,21,Fare you?"
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
