PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781714895
OL,3,C'I'm the boss', says Trump as he meets
OL,4,CG7 leaders on last day of summit
OL,6,F"Good, thank you," Trump responds as
OL,7,Fhe shakes Macron's hand and sits down.
OL,9,FThe G7 leaders were closing the formal
OL,10,Ftalks with sessions on the future of
OL,11,Fartificial intelligence and fostering
OL,12,Feconomic growth.
OL,14,FThe summit comes as Trump clinched a
OL,15,Fpeace deal with Iran, which he says
OL,16,Fwill see oil flow freely again through
OL,17,Fthe Strait of Hormuz, the vital global
OL,18,Fshipping route.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
