FL,311,300,200,140,000,100
PN,31003
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781714895
OL,3,C'I'm the boss', says Trump as he meets
OL,4,CG7 leaders on last day of summit
OL,6,FThe US president said the Strait would
OL,7,Fbe fully opened on Friday once the
OL,8,Fdeal is signed in Switzerland.
OL,10,FSpeaking on Tuesday morning, Trump
OL,11,Fsaid that the deal is "all signed" and
OL,12,Fpromised that "Iran will never have a
OL,13,Fnuclear weapon".
OL,15,FIt is understood that this temporary
OL,16,Fdeal will last for 60 days in an
OL,17,Fattempt to address Iran's nuclear
OL,18,Fprogramme and open the Strait.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
