CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781714895
OL,3,C'I'm the boss', says Trump as he meets
OL,4,CG7 leaders on last day of summit
OL,6,FBoth the US and Israel launched the
OL,7,Fwar on February 28, striking numerous
OL,8,Ftargets in Iran, with Iran responding
OL,9,Fby blocking the Strait and attacking
OL,10,FUS allies in the region.
OL,12,FStarmer spoke to ITV News at the G7
OL,13,Fsummit, saying that British ships will
OL,14,Fbe in the Strait of Hormuz when it is
OL,15,F"safe" to do so
OL,17,FLeaders at the summit threw their
OL,18,Fsupport behind Trump's deal even
OL,19,Fthough very little detail has been
OL,20,Foffered about how it would be
OL,21,Fimplemented.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
