OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781714895
OL,3,C'I'm the boss', says Trump as he meets
OL,4,CG7 leaders on last day of summit
OL,6,FIn a declaration issued overnight, the
OL,7,Fleaders called the deal a "historic
OL,8,Fopportunity to prevent Iran from
OL,9,Facquiring any nuclear weapon and
OL,10,Ftackling the threats related to its
OL,11,Fregional and ballistic activities".
OL,13,FThey said that they were "ready to
OL,14,Fcontribute to its implementation,"
OL,15,Falthough neither the White House nor
OL,16,FIran has released the text of the
OL,17,Fagreement.
OL,26,@uD@ZOUvD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
