PN,31007
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F310A1781714895
OL,3,C'I'm the boss', says Trump as he meets
OL,4,CG7 leaders on last day of summit
OL,6,FBoth Starmer and members of his
OL,7,Fgovernment have been heavily critical
OL,8,Fof the war in Iran, which began after
OL,9,Fjoint attacks by the US and Israel in
OL,10,FFebruary, with the PM saying he was
OL,11,F"sick and tired" of seeing energy
OL,12,Fbills rise as a result of it, whilst
OL,13,Fother ministers described it as a
OL,14,F"mistake".
OL,16,FThe US leader later plans to make a
OL,17,Fstop for a glitzy dinner at the Palace
OL,18,Fof Versailles outside of Paris before
OL,19,Fhe heads back to Washington.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/7
